quran[59]{c,v,t}:
  26,52,"Men Wahayini faade e Muusaa: \"∆äum woni ro∆īidu e jeyaa…ďe Am …ďen. Pellet, onon ko on jokkitetee…ďe"
  26,53,Fir'awna nuli ka ca'e moo…ďoo…ďe
  26,54,"[O wi'i:] Pellet, …ďee ko …ďe mojobun pamarun"
  26,55,"Pellet, kam…ďe hi…ďe tikkinnde men"
  26,56,Enen non en fow ko en rentii…ďe
  26,57,Men yaltini …ďe immorde e gese e can…ói
  26,58,E ngaluuji e √Īii…ďirde teddunde
  26,59,"Ko wano nii, Men ronini …óum …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen"
  26,60,∆Āe jokki…ďe ka pu…óal
  26,61,"Tuma nde jamaaji …óin …óin yi'ndirnoo, yim…ďe Muusaa …ďen wi'i: \"Enen en hewtoyte"
  26,62,"O maaki: \"∆äum wa…óataa, pellet, Joomi am no wonndi e am O fewnay lam"
  26,63,"Men Wahayini e Muusaa, …óum woni piyir tuggordu maa…óa ndun maayo ngon, ngo seekii seekol kala seekol na foti e tulde mawnde"
  26,64,Men …ďanni ton heddii…ďe …ďen
  26,65,Men danndi Muusaa e wonndu…ďe e makko …ďen fow ma…ď…ďe
  26,66,Refti Men yooli heddii …ďe …ďen
  26,67,"Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ďur…ďe heewude e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gom…óin…ďe"
  26,68,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  26,69,Janngan …ďe kumpital fii Ibraahiima
  26,70,Tuma nde o wi'annoo ben makko e yim…ďe makko …ďen; ko hon…óum rewoton
  26,71,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Me…óen rewude sanamuuji, men √Īallay ufinanaade …ói"
  26,72,"O maaki: \"Yalli hi…ói nanana on, nde noddoton"
  26,73,Kaa hi…ói nafa on maa…óum …ói lorra on
  26,74,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Ko woni, men tawii baabiraa…ďe amen …ďen konii …ďe golliraynoo"
  26,75,"O maaki: \"Enee, on yi'ii kon ko wonu…óon e rewude"
  26,76,Onon e baabiraa…ďe moo…óon adinoo…ďe …ďen
  26,77,"Pellet, kam…ďe ko …ďe ay…ďe am, si wanaa Jooma winndire nden"
  26,78,"On Tagu…óo lam, ko Kanko fewnata lam"
  26,79,On ko Kanko √Īamminta lam O yarnan-mi
  26,80,"Si mi nawnii, ko Kanko sellinta lam"
  26,81,E On waray…óo lam refti O wurnitan mi
  26,82,"On Mo mi tam∆īinii kadi nde O yaafatoomi goopi am …óin √Ďalnde [njo…ďdi] Diina kan"
  26,83,"Joomam, okkam Ganndal wattidaa mi e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen. @Corrected"
  26,84,Wa…óanaa lam …óemngal goongungal ka sakkitii…ďe …ďen
  26,85,Wa…óaa mi jeyaa…óo e ronoo…ďe Aljanna Neemaaji …óin
  26,86,"Yawtanaa baaba am, pellet, kanko o laatinoke jeyaa…óo e majju…ďe …ďen"
  26,87,Wata A hersinoyam √Ďalnde …ďe Immital
  26,88,√Ďalnde nde jawdi e …ďi…ó…ďe nafataa
  26,89,Si wanaa on ardu…óo ka Alla e …ďernde hisunde
  26,90,Aljanna on …ďatinanee huloo…ďe Alla …ďen
  26,91,Jahiim ngen fe√Ī√Īinanee bew…ďe …ďen
  26,92,"∆Āe wi'nee: \"Honto woni ko laatino…óon kon hi…óon rewa"
  26,93,Gaanin Alla? Taw si …ói wallay on maa…óum …ói wallay hoore majji
  26,94,∆Āe hippee e nder magge kan…ďe e bew…ďe …ďen
  26,95,E konnuuji ibliisa …óin …ói fow majji
  26,96,∆Āe wi'i tawi kam…ďe hi…ďe wennjondira nder ton
  26,97,"Men woondirii Alla, men woniino e nder majjere …ďanngunde"
  26,98,Tuma nde men fonnunoo on e Jooma winndere nden
  26,99,Majjinaali men si wonaa bon…ďe …ďen
  26,100,Alanaa men tefoo…ďe
  26,101,Wanaa kadi gi…óo √Īallam…ďereejo(tigi tigi)
  26,102,"Sinndo no woodannoo men rutteede, men laatoo jeyaa…ďe e gom…óin…ďe …ďen"
  26,103,"Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ďur…ďe heewu…ďe e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gom…óin…ďe"
  26,104,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  26,105,Yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen fenni Nulaa…ďe …ďen
  26,106,"Tuma nde Nuuhu musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on wi'annoo …ďe: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,107,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo e moo…óon hoolaa…óo"
  26,108,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,109,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óum njo…ďdi, njo…ďdi am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,110,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi